privacy%20protections%20do%20still%20apply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Trump%2C%20the%20United%20States%20has%20%26quot%3Bpicked%20up%20their%20cowboy%20hat%20again%2C%20it's%20a%20complete%20Wild%20West%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Yael%20Cohen-Hadria%2C%20a%20digital%20lawyer%20at%20consultancy%20EY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20has%20effectively%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20not%20doing%20this%20law%20anymore...%20we're%20setting%20all%20our%20algorithms%20running%20and%20going%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20government%20is%20still%20developing%20a%20formal%20law%20on%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20set%20of%20%26quot%3BInterim%20Measures%26quot%3B%20requires%20that%20AI%20respects%20personal%20and%20business%20interests%2C%20does%20not%20use%20personal%20information%20without%20consent%2C%20signposts%20AI-generated%20images%20and%20videos%2C%20and%20protects%20users'%20physical%20and%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20must%20also%20%26quot%3Badhere%20to%20core%20socialist%20values%26quot%3B%20--%20with%20strong%20language%20against%20AI%20generating%20content%20threatening%20the%20ruling%20Communist%20Party%20or%20China's%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%2C%20whose%20frugal%20yet%20powerful%20R1%20model%20shocked%20the%20world%20last%20month%2C%20is%20an%20example%2C%20resisting%20questions%20about%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20or%20the%201989%20crushing%20of%20pro-democracy%20demonstrations%20in%20Tiananmen%20Square.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20regulating%20business%20closely%2C%20especially%20foreigners%2C%20China's%20government%20will%20grant%20itself%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20exceptions%26quot%3B%20to%20its%20own%20rules%2C%20Cohen-Hadria%20predicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEuropean%20Union%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20both%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ethical%20philosophy%20of%20respecting%20citizens%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20European%20regulation%26quot%3B%2C%20Cohen-Hadria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20has%20their%20share%20of%20responsibility%2C%20the%20provider%2C%20whoever%20deploys%20(AI)%2C%20even%20the%20final%20consumer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20directly%20concerning%20AI%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BAI%20Act%26quot%3B%20passed%20in%20March%202024%20--%20some%20of%20whose%20provisions%20apply%20from%20this%20week%20--%20is%20the%20most%20comprehensive%20regulation%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20AI%20for%20predictive%20policing%20based%20on%20profiling%20and%20systems%20that%20use%20biometric%20information%20to%20infer%20an%20individual's%20race%2C%20religion%20or%20sexual%20orientation%20are%20banned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20takes%20a%20risk-based%20approach%3A%20if%20a%20system%20is%20high-risk%2C%20a%20company%20has%20a%20stricter%20set%20of%20obligations%20to%20fulfil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEU%20leaders%20have%20argued%20that%20clear%2C%20comprehensive%20rules%20will%20make%20life%20easier%20for%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECohen-Hadria%20pointed%20to%20strong%20protections%20for%20intellectual%20property%20and%20efforts%20to%20allow%20data%20to%20circulate%20more%20freely%20while%20granting%20citizens%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20can%20access%20a%20lot%20of%20data%20easily%2C%20I%20can%20create%20better%20things%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20China%2C%20India%20--%20co-host%20of%20next%20week's%20summit%20--%20has%20a%20law%20on%20personal%20data%20but%20no%20specific%20text%20governing%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECases%20of%20harm%20originating%20from%20generative%20AI%20have%20been%20tackled%20with%20existing%20legislation%20on%20defamation%2C%20privacy%2C%20copyright%20infringement%20and%20cybercrime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20knows%20the%