%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fintrospect-instead-of-insulting-maharashtra-cm-fadnavis-slams-rahul-over-maharashtra-poll-allegations%2Farticleshow%2F117901020.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Starts%20Deporting%20Indian%20Migrants%20Amid%20Trump's%20Border%20Crackdown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20US%20military%20plane%20began%20deporting%20Indian%20migrants%2C%20implementing%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20hardline%20stance%20against%20an%20estimated%2011%20million%20undocumented%20migrants%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20C-17%20aircraft%20carrying%20205%20Indian%20nationals%20departed%20from%20San%20Antonio%2C%20Texas%20departed%20around%203%20am%20IST.%20Sources%20told%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20all%20Indians%20on%20board%20the%20flight%20were%20verified%20by%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20farthest%20destination%20of%20US%20military%20flights%20deporting%20migrants%2C%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20stating%20flights%20to%20deport%20over%205%2C000%20migrants%20from%20El%20Paso%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20San%20Diego%2C%20California.%20So%20far%2C%20military%20aircraft%20have%20flown%20migrants%20to%20Guatemala%2C%20Peru%20and%20Honduras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20launched%20the%20military%20deportation%20flights%20last%20week%20as%20part%20of%20his%20emergency%20declaration%20on%20immigration%2C%20so%20far%20sending%20six%20planeloads%20of%20migrants%20on%20flights%20to%20Latin%20America.%20Only%20four%20landed%2C%20all%20of%20them%20in%20Guatemala%2C%20after%20Colombia%20refused%20to%20let%20two%20US%20C-17%20cargo%20aircraft%20land%20and%20instead%20sent%20its%20own%20planes%20to%20collect%20migrants%20following%20a%20standoff%20with%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20history%2C%20we%20are%20locating%20and%20loading%20illegal%20aliens%20into%20military%20aircraft%20and%20flying%20them%20back%20to%20the%20places%20from%20which%20they%20came%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20reporters%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20President%20had%20said%20after%20a%20call%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20that%20the%20latter%20%26quot%3Bwill%20do%20what's%20right%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taking%20back%20illegal%20Indian%20immigrants%20from%20America.%20Bloomberg%20News%20reported%20that%20India%20and%20the%20US%20have%20identified%20some%2018%2C000%20Indian%20migrants%20who%20are%20in%20the%20US%20illegally.%20Indians%20account%20for%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20skilled%20worker%20H-1B%20visas%20issued%20by%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deportations%20and%20border%20control%20come%20after%20Trump%20had%20said%20on%20his%20first%20day%20in%20office%20that%20he%20will%20deport%20%26quot%3Bmillions%20and%20millions%26quot%3B%20of%20migrants%2C%20while%20declaring%20a%20national%20emergency%20at%20the%20southern%20border.%20Day%20within%20him%20assuming%20the%20top%20post%2C%20the%20the%20US%20Congress%20approved%20a%20bill%20that%20would%20require%20the%20detention%20and%20deportation%20of%20undocumented%20migrants%20who%20enter%20the%20country%20without%20authorisation%20and%20are%20charged%20with%20certain%20crimes.%20Even%20during%20his%20campaign%20trail%2C%20he%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20am%20reelected%2C%20we%20will%20begin%20the%20largest%20deportation%20operation%20in%20American%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20often%20used%20the%20military%20to%20implement%20his%20immigration%20agenda.%20He%20has%20sent%20troops%20to%20the%20US%20Mexico%20border%2C%20used%20military%20bases%20to%20house%20migrants%20and%20military%20aircraft%20to%20fly%20them%20out%20of%20the%20US.%20However%2C%20Reuters%20reported%20that%20a%20military%20deportation%20flight%20to%20Guatemala%20last%20week%20likely%20cost%20at%20least%20%244%2C675%20per%20migrant.%20That%20is%20more%20than%20five%20times%20the%20%24853%20cost%20of%20a%20one-way%20first%20class%20ticket%20on%20American%20Airlines%20from%20El%20Paso%2C%20Texas%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%20It%20is%20also%20significantly%20higher%20than%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20commercial%20charter%20flight%20by%20US%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20immigration%2C%20Trump%20also%20announced%20a%20string%20of%20tariffs%20on%20Canada%2C%20Mexico%20and%20China%2C%20adding%20that%20similar%20measures%20are%20in%20the%20works%20for%20Europe%20too.%20Tariff%20hikes%20on%20Canada%20will%20also%20be%20delayed%20by%20a%20month%20as%20it%20brought%20itself%20a%20brief%20reprieve%20with%20a%20promise%20of%20%241.3%20billion%20on%20measures%20to%20stop%20the%20flow%20of%20drugs%20and%20undocumented%20migrants%20into%20the%20US%20through%20the%20northern%20border.%20Mexico%20won%20itself%20a%20similar%20reprieve%20earlier%20with%20the%20commitment%20of%2010%2C000%20troops%20to%20its%20border%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20tariffs%20of%2025%20per%20cent%20on%20imports%20from%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20were%20to%20go%20into%20effect%20from%20Tuesday%20over%20the%20flow%20of%20undocumented%20migrants%20and%20drugs%20into%20the%20US%20through%20their%20borders.%20A%20lower%2010%20per%20cent%20hike%20is%20coming%20in%20China%2C%20but%20there%20were%20no%20talks%20ahead%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738640940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-12%2Fscqph3vo_uscanada-borderafp_625x300_12_December_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-military-plane-departs-with-indian-migrants-on-board-report-7628681%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20C-17%20aircraft%20carrying%20205%20Indian%20nationals%20departed%20from%20San%20Antonio%2C%20Texas%20departed%20around%203%20am%20IST.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-military-plane-departs-with-indian-migrants-on-board-report-7628681%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stock%20market%20today%3A%20BSE%20Sensex%20rises%20over%20700%20points%3B%20Nifty50%20above%2023%2C550%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738640926000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117900419%2Cimgsize-83112.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fstock-market-today-bse-sensex-nifty50-february-04-2025-dalal-street-indian-equities-global-markets%2Farticleshow%2F117900312.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20market%20today%3A%20BSE%20Sensex%20and%20Nifty50%2C%20the%20Indian%20equity%20benchmark%20indices%2C%20surged%20in%20trade%20on%20Tuesday.%20While%20BSE%20Sensex%20was%20above%2077%2C800%2C%20Nifty50%20was%20above%2023%2C550.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fstock-market-today-bse-sensex-nifty50-february-04-2025-dalal-street-indian-equities-global-markets%2Farticleshow%2F117900312.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ashwin's%20Blunt%20Message%20To%20Rohit%2C%20Wants%20Change%20In%20Champions%20Trophy%20Squad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Champions%20Trophy%20squad%20has%20been%20out%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20certain%20players'%20performances%20in%20the%20recently-concluded%20T20I%20series%20against%20England%20have%20triggered%20talks%20of%20'changes'.%20While%20India%20have%20picked%20up%204%20spinners%20for%20the%20marquee%20ICC%20event%2C%20veteran%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20asked%20for%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Varun%20Chak