v.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others%20to%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20existing%20squad%2C%20if%20a%20seamer%20goes%20out%20and%20Varun%20comes%20in%2C%20it%20will%20be%20an%20added%20spinner%20(five).%20I%20don't%20know%20who%20they%20would%20want%20to%20drop%20(if%20they%20think%20about%20getting%20Varun%20in).%20We%20will%20wait%20and%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20feeling%20that%20Varun%20might%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20play%20in%20the%20ODI%20series%20between%20India%20and%20England.%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20an%20easy%20call%20to%20take%20him%20directly%20to%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20He%20has%20not%20played%20ODIs.%20I%20have%20a%20feeling%20they%20will%20give%20him%20a%20chance%20in%20the%20India%20vs%20England%20ODI%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20don't%20give%20him%20a%20chance%20here%2C%20then%20it's%20difficult.%20But%2C%20nevertheless%2C%20I%20congratulate%20Varun%20for%20his%20first%20Player%20of%20the%20Tournament%20award.%20He%20is%20the%20Chakravarthy%20of%20T20I%20cricket%20at%20the%20moment.%20I%20wish%20he%20grows%20more%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738640580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fn39a84hg_r-ashwin-and-rohit-sharma-bcci_625x300_04_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fr-ashwin-sends-blunt-message-to-rohit-sharma-wants-change-in-indias-champions-trophy-squad-7629202%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22R%20Ashwin%20wants%20one%20change%20in%20India's%20Champions%20Trophy%20squad%20but%20isn't%20sure%20which%20player%20will%20be%20dropped.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fr-ashwin-sends-blunt-me