ster%20Justin%20Trudeau%20and%20Mexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20struck%20deals%20for%20a%20postponement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20that%20after%20%26quot%3Bvery%20friendly%26quot%3B%20talks%20with%20Sheinbaum%20he'd%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20pause%26quot%3B%20the%20tariffs%20on%20Mexico%2C%20and%20that%20his%20counterpart%20had%20agreed%20to%20send%2010%2C000%20troops%20to%20the%20US-Mexico%20frontier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20appeared%20higher%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%2C%20but%20afer%20two%20separate%20calls%20Trump%20later%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20pleased%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20announcing%20a%2030-day%20halt%20in%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCanada%20has%20agreed%20to%20ensure%20we%20have%20a%20secure%20Northern%20Border%2C%20and%20to%20finally%20end%20the%20deadly%20scourge%20of%20drugs%20like%20Fentanyl%20that%20have%20been%20pouring%20into%20our%20Country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalks%20on%20final%20deals%20would%20continue%20with%20both%20countries%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20said%20after%20the%20%26quot%3Bgood%20call%26quot%3B%20that%20Canada%20deploy%20nearly%2010%2C000%20frontline%20officers%20to%20help%20secure%20the%20border%2C%20list%20drug%20cartels%20as%20terrorists%2C%20appoint%20a%20%26quot%3BFentanyl%20Czar%26quot%3B%20and%20crack%20down%20on%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20just%20had%20a%20good%20call%20with%20President%20Trump.%20Canada%20is%20implementing%20our%20%241.3%20billion%20border%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20reinforcing%20the%20border%20with%20new%20choppers%2C%20technology%20and%20personnel%2C%20enhanced%20coordination%20with%20our%20American%20partners%2C%20and%20increased%20resources%20to%20stop%20the%20flow%20of%20fentanyl.%20Nearly%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Justin%20Trudeau%20(%40JustinTrudeau)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJustinTrudeau%2Fstatus%2F1886529228193022429%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%203%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20clear%20the%20real%20extent%20of%20the%20changes%20on%20the%20Canadian%20border%2C%20given%20that%20just%20this%20December%20authorities%20there%20said%20they%20already%20had%208%2C500%20personnel%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStocks%20slump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20remains%20in%20the%20firing%20line%20for%20Trump%20tariffs.%20It%20faces%20a%20further%2010%20percent%20duty%20on%20top%20of%20existing%20levies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20president%20said%20last-minute%20talks%20between%20Washington%20and%20Beijing%20will%20likely%20be%20held%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20in%20the%20next%2024%20hours%26quot%3B%20to%20avoid%20new%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%2C%20China%20and%20Mexico%20are%20the%20United%20States's%20three%20biggest%20trading%20partners%2C%20and%20Trump's%20threatened%20tariffs%20have%20sent%20shock%20waves%20through%20the%20global%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWall%20Street's%20three%20main%20indices%20fell%20sharply%20in%20early%20deals%2C%20but%20clawed%20back%20ground%20after%20Trump's%20announcement%20on%20the%20Mexico%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20London%2C%20Paris%20and%20Frankfurt%20stock%20markets%20finished%20in%20the%20red%20as%20Trump%20warned%20over%20the%20weekend%20that%20the%20European%20Union%20would%20be%20next%20in%20the%20firing%20line%20and%20did%20not%20rule%20out%20tariffs%20on%20Britain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mexican%20peso%20and%20Canadian%20dollar%20also%20sank%20against%20the%20greenback%2C%20while%20oil%20jumped%20despite%20Trump%20limiting%20the%20levy%20on%20Canada's%20energy%20imports%20at%2010%20percent%20to%20avoid%20a%20spike%20in%20fuel%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20earlier%20there%20had%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bheck%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20talks%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20trade%20war%2C%20this%20is%20a%20drug%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20National%20Economic%20Council%20Director%20Kevin%20Hassett%20told%20CNBC%2C%20complaining%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Canadians%20appeared%20to%20have%20misunderstood%20the%20plain%20language.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20US%20government%20figures%20show%20that%20only%20a%20minimal%20quantity%20of%20drugs%20comes%20via%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E51st%20state%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20had%20vowed%20to%20respond%20strongly%20to%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20most%20populous%20province%20Ontario%20on%20Monday%20had%20banned%20US%20firms%20from%20bidding%20on%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20government%20contracts%20--%20and%20dumped%20a%20deal%20with%20Trump%20ally%20Elon%20Musk's%20Starlink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20upped%20the%20pressure%20recently%20by%20calling%20Canada's%20existence%20into%20question%20--%20once%20again%20calling%20on%20Monday%20for%20it%20to%20become%20the%2051st%20US%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20political%20crisis%20in%20the%20Canadian%20government%20over%20Trump's%20tariff%20threats%20led%20to%20Trudeau%20announcing%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20he%20would%20quit%20too.%20Canadians%20now%20face%20elections%20as%20early%20as%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20president%20--%20who%20has%20said%20that%20tariff%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20beautiful%20word%20in%20the%20dictionary%26quot%3B%20--%20is%20going%20even%20further%20in%20his%20second%20term%20on%20the%20levies%20than%20he%20did%20in%20his%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20insisted%20that%20the%20impact%20would%20be%20borne%20by%20foreign%20exporters%20without%20being%20passed%20on%20to%20American%20consumers%2C%20despite%20most%20experts%20saying%20the%20contrary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20billionaire%2078-y