s%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738633380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fmrnut6gg_buttler-and-samson-bcci_625x300_03_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2025%2Findia-played-with-12-players-england-great-cries-foul-as-hosts-secure-4-1-series-win-7622310%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20England%20captain%20Michael%20Vaughan%20had%20to%20eat%20his%20own%20words%20after%20India%20secured%20a%204-1%20win%20in%20T20I%20series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2025%2Findia-played-with-12-players-england-great-cries-foul-as-hosts-secure-4-1-series-win-7622310%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lung%20Cancer%20Cases%20In%20Never-Smokers%20On%20The%20Rise%3A%20Lancet%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECases%20of%20lung%20cancer%20among%20those%20who%20never%20smoked%20is%20on%20the%20rise%20and%20air%20pollution%20could%20be%20contributing%20to%20the%20increase%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20was%20published%20in%20The%20Lancet%20Respiratory%20Medicine%20journal%20on%20World%20Cancer%20Day%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%2C%20including%20those%20from%20the%20International%20Agency%20for%20Research%20on%20Cancer%20(IARC)%2C%20World%20Health%20Organization%2C%20analysed%20data%2C%20including%20those%20from%20the%20Global%20Cancer%20Observatory%202022%20dataset%2C%20to%20estimate%20national-level%20lung%20cancer%20cases%20for%20four%20subtypes%20--%20adenocarcinoma%2C%20squamous%20cell%20carcinoma%2C%20small-%20and%20large-cell%20carcinoma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20that%20adenocarcinoma%20--%20a%20cancer%20that%20starts%20in%20glands%20that%20produce%20fluids%20such%20as%20mucus%20and%20digestive%20ones%20--%20has%20become%20the%20dominant%20subtype%20among%20both%20men%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sub-type%20of%20lung%20cancer%20was%20also%20found%20to%20account%20for%2053-70%20per%20cent%20of%20lung%20cancer%20cases%20in%202022%20among%20never-smokers%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20the%20other%20sub-types%20of%20lung%20cancer%2C%20risk%20of%20adenocarcinoma%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20weakly%20related%20with%20cigarette%20smoking%2C%20the%20authors%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20smoking%20prevalence%20continues%20to%20decline%20in%20many%20countries%20worldwide%2C%20the%20proportion%20of%20lung%20cancer%20in%20people%20who%20have%20never%20smoked%20has%20increased%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChanges%20in%20smoking%20patterns%20and%20exposure%20to%20air%20pollution%20are%20among%20the%20main%20determinants%20of%20the%20changing%20risk%20profile%20of%20lung%20cancer%20incidence%20by%20subtype%20that%20we%20see%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20lead%20author%20Freddie%20Bray%2C%20head%20of%20the%20cancer%20surveillance%20branch%20at%20IARC%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELung%20cancer%20is%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20cancer-related%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%26quot%3Blung%20cancer%20in%20people%20who%20have%20never%20smoked%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20the%20fifth%20leading%20cause%20of%20cancer-related%20mortality%20worldwide%2C%20occurring%20almost%20exclusively%20as%20adenocarcinoma%20and%20most%20commonly%20in%20women%20and%20Asian%20populations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202022%2C%20we%20estimated%20that%20there%20were%20908%20630%20new%20cases%20of%20lung%20cancer%20worldwide%20among%20female%20individuals%2C%20of%20which%20541%20971%20(59.7%20per%20cent)%20were%20adenocarcinoma%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20among%20the%20women%20diagnosed%20with%20adenocarcinoma%2C%2080%2C378%20could%20be%20traced%20to%20ambient%20particulate%20matter%20(PM)%20pollution%20in%202022%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20diverging%20trends%20by%20sex%20in%20recent%20generations%20offer%20insights%20to%20cancer%20prevention%20specialists%20and%20policy-makers%20seeking%20to%20develop%20and%20implement%20tobacco%20and%20air%20pollution%20control%20strategies%20tailored%20to%20high-risk%20populations%2C%26quot%3B%20Bray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%202019%2C%20almost%20everyone%20in%20the%20world%20is%20estimated%20to%20live%20in%20areas%20not%20meeting%20the%20WHO%20air%20quality%20criteria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738633260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Flung-cancer-_625x300_1528186696821.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Flung-cancer-cases-in-never-smokers-on-the-rise-lancet-study-7628361%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cases%20of%20lung%20cancer%20among%20those%20who%20never%20smoked%20is%20on%20the%20rise%20and%20air%20pollution%20could%20be%20contributing%20to%20the%20increase%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Flung-cancer-cases-in-never-smokers-on-the-rise-lancet-study-7628361%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20Breaks%20Silence%20On%20Rift%20Rumours%20During%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELiving%20up%20to%20his%20reputation%20of%20not%20mincing%20words%2C%20India%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20mocked%20those%20spreading%20rumours%20of%20a%20rift%20in%20the%20Indian%20team.%20On%20Team%20India's%20previous%20tour%2C%20away%20to%20Australia%2C%20reports%20of%20there%20being%20divide%20in%20the%20Indian%20team%20emerged.%20As%20results%20went%20against%20the%20Indian%20team%20Down%20Under%2C%20the%20defeats%20against%20Australia%20further%20fuelled%20the%20rumours%2C%20but%20Gambhir%20decided%20to%20maintain%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20matter.%20However%2C%20after%20helping%20the%20Indian%20team%20secure%20a%204-1%20T20I%20series%20win%20against%20England%2C%20Gambhir%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20back%20to%20those%20spreading%20the%20rumours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20post-match%20chat%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%205th%20T20I%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Gambhir%20highlighted%20how%20the%20nature%20of%20results%20trigger%20different%20kind%20of%20rumours%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%20with%20each%20other.%20More%20importantly%2C%20a%20month%20back%2C%20there%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20other%20rumours%20flying%20around%20(laughs).%20That's%20what%20Indian%20cricket%20is%20all%20about.%20There%20will%20be%20so%20many%20things%20said%20about%20the%20dressing%20room%20when%20things%20are%20not%20going%20okay.%20But%20once%20results%20start%20going%20in%20your%20favour%2C%20things%20start%20falling%20in%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20Gambhir%20didn't%20call%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20rumours%20to%20be%20false.%20Rather%2C%20just%20went%20about%20explaining%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20also%20said%20the%20team%20is%20ready%20to%20push%20the%20barriers%20in%20T20%20Internationals%20with%20the%20adoption%20of%20a%20fresh%20%26quot%3Bhigh-risk%2C%20high-reward%26quot%3B%20approach%2C%20and%20the%20target%20is%20now%20%26quot%3Bto%20get%20250-260%20regularly%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fourth%20T20I%20at%20Pune%2C%20India%20kept%20attacking%20England%20despite%20losing%20wickets%20to%20eventually%20set%20a%20match-winning%20181%20for%209%2C%20and%20at%20Mumbai%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20hosts%20raced%20to%20247%20for%209%2C%20their%20fourth%20highest%20total%20in%20this%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20kind%20of%20T20%20cricket%20we%20want%20to%20play.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20fear%20losing%20a%20game%20of%20cricket.%20We%20want%20to%20play%20high-risk%2C%20high-reward%20cricket.%20And%20these%20guys%20have%20adopted%20that%20ideology%20really%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gambhir%20told%20the%20host%20broadcaster%20after%20the%20match%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20said%20they%20are%20looking%20to%20post%20tall%20totals%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20250%20in%20every%20game%2C%20and%20he%20doesn't%20mind%20getting%20out%20for%20a%20low%20score%20in%20some%20matches%20while%20attempting%20to%20achieve%20the%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20try%20and%20get%20to%20250-260%20regularly.%20And%20in%20trying%20to%20do%20that%2C%20there'll%20be%20games%20where%20we'll%20get%20bundled%20out%20for%20120-130.%20And%20that%20is%20what%20T20%20cricket%20is%20all%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20and%20until%20you%20don't%20play%20that%20high-risk%20cricket%2C%20you%20won't%20get%20those%20big%20rewards%20as%20well.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20I%20think%20we're%20on%20the%20right%20track.%20Come%20those%20big%20tournaments%2C%20we%20want%20to%20continue%20playing%20this%20way%20and%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20fear%20losing%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738633260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fdsts7h3g_gautam-gambhir-rohit-sharma-afp_625x300_27_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-breaks-silence-on-rift-rumours-during-border-gavaskar-trophy-7621635%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rumours%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20not%20being%20on%20the%20same%20page%20had%20stormed%20social%20media%