a%20shopper%20at%20the%20company's%20recently%20opened%20Grapevine%20store%2C%20which%20doesn't%20feature%20traditional%20checkout%20lanes.%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWalmart-owned%20Sam's%20Club%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Btreasure%20trove%26quot%3B%20of%20purchasing%20data.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Chris%20Nicholas%20told%20BI%20this%20data%20is%20powering%20the%20company's%20big%20push%20into%20experiential%20retail.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENicholas%20has%20named%20Diana%20Marshall%20to%20be%20his%20new%20chief%20experience%20officer%2C%20or%20CXO%20%E2%80%94%20a%20relatively%20rare%20title%20in%20retail.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sam's%20Club%20CEO%20Chris%20Nicholas%20saw%20the%20news%20that%20his%20company%20had%20unseated%20perennial%20winner%20Costco%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsams-club-beats-costco-customer-satisfaction-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop-rated%20retailer%20for%20customer%20satisfaction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20was%20understandably%20pleased%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20didn't%20bask%20in%20the%20feeling%20for%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20more%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BNothing%20happens%20by%20accident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jump%20in%20Sam's%20Club's%20score%20%E2%80%94%20leapfrogging%20Costco's%20similarly%20strong%20rating%20%E2%80%94%20follows%20a%20busy%20year%20in%20which%20the%20Walmart-owned%20warehouse%20club%20rolled%20out%20new%20futuristic%20tech%20intended%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsams-club-ai-cart-scanners-technology-automatically-ring-up-items-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20shopping%20easier%20and%20more%20enjoyable%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20one%20year%20ago%20that%20the%20company%20announced%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsams-club-will-scan-cart-instead-of-checking-receipt-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-powered%20exit%20gateways%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20doing%20away%20with%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20frustrations%20of%20shopping%20at%20a%20warehouse%20club%3A%20receipt%20checks%20at%20the%20exit.%20And%20in%20October%2C%20Sam's%20Club%20opened%20its%20first%20location%20without%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsams-club-opens-first-new-location-in-years-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20checkout%20lanes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20bold%20bet%20as%20some%20other%20retailers%2C%20like%20Amazon%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazons-just-walk-out-pullback-shows-ai-way-to-go%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epulled%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20using%20AI-powered%20%26quot%3BJust%20Walk%20Out%26quot%3B%20cashierless%20tech%20at%20its%20Fresh%20stores%20in%20favor%20of%20smart%20carts%2C%20and%20others%2C%20including%20Target%2C%20have%20put%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-self-checkout-limit-10-items-less-twice-as-fast-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elimits%20on%20self-service%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20many%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Sam's%20Club%2C%20it's%20part%20of%20a%20longer-term%20strategy%20to%20give%20it%20a%20high-tech%20edge%20in%20the%20historically%20low-tech%20warehouse%20retail%20segment.%20The%20company%20says%20more%20than%20half%20of%20customers%20at%20locations%20with%20the%20AI%20scan-and-go%20option%20use%20the%20tech%2C%20and%20it's%20helped%20the%20shoppers%20get%20out%20the%20door%2023%25%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20all%20a%20result%20of%20working%20really%20hard%20at%20the%20inputs%20and%20then%20the%20outputs%20heal%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicholas%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20we're%20building%20digital%20products%20for%20our%20associates%20as%20well%20as%20for%20our%20members%2C%20it%20means%20you%20create%20connected%20experiences%20that%20allow%20people%20to%20self-solve%20and%20work%20together%20on%20having%20a%20delightful%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20advantage%20that%20warehouse%20clubs%2C%20in%20general%2C%20have%20over%20their%20traditional%20retail%20counterparts%20is%20much%20more%20detailed%20information%20about%20shoppers'%20purchase%20histories%2C%20as%20a%20membership%20is%20required%20for%20every%20purchase.%20(General%20retailers%20can%20still%20piece%20together%20a%20profile%20using%20payment%20or%20loyalty%20cards%2C%20of%20course.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Sam's%20Club%2C%20however%2C%20member%20profiles%20are%20augmented%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsams-club-store-without-checkouts-grapevine-texas-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emassive%20amounts%20of%20digital%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20plus%20additional%20insights%20from%20the%2050%2C000-strong%20Members%20Mark%20community%20of%20shoppers%20that%20share%20feedback%20on%20products%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20certainly%20true%20that%20we've%20had%20this%20treasure%20trove%20of%20data%2C%20and%20we've%20been%20on%20this%20journey%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20to%20really%20hone%20it%20so%20that%20we%20understand%20and%20can%20use%20this%20data%20more%20specifically%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicholas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Sam's%20Club%20doesn't%20publicly%20report%20detailed%20financial%20results%2C%20one%20consistent%20bright%20spot%20in%20Walmart's%20earnings%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20been%20the%20growth%20of%20revenue%20from%20memberships%20and%20from%20retail%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20Nicholas%20notes%20that%20much%20of%20the%20tech%20investment%20expenses%20for%20Sam's%20Club%20are%20borne%20by%20Walmart's%20deeper%20pockets%2C%20since%20the%20club%20has%20often%20served%20as%20an%20innovation%20lab%20for%20the%20world's%20largest%20retailer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20of%20this%20data%2C%20Nicholas%20says%20he%20decided%20to%20put%20one%20person%20in%20charge%20of%20turning%20it%20into%20a%20more%20effective%20flywheel%20for%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20faster%20the%20flywheel%20spins%2C%20the%20more%20that%20virtuous%20circle%20helps%20you%20open%20up%20even%20a%20deeper%20gap%20versus%20everybody%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20spirit%2C%20Sam's%20Club%20has%20appointed%20Diana%20Marshall%2C%20who%20was%20previously%20chief%20growth%20officer%2C%20as%20its%20new%20chief%20experience%20officer.%20Marshall%20will%20report%20directly%20to%20Nicholas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECXO%20is%20a%20title%20that%20Constellation%20Research%20founder%20Ray%20Wang%20told%20BI%20is%20more%20typically%20found%20reporting%20to%20the%20CEO%20at%20tech%2C%20hospitality%2C%20travel%2C%20or%20financial%20services%20companies%20than%20at%20retailers.%20Sam's%20Club%20said%20it%20consulted%20with%20Wang%20on%20the%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20chief%20experience%20officers%2C%20in%20general%2C%20playing%20a%20bigger%20and%20bigger%20role%20because%20you're%20basically%20differentiating%20on%20time%20and%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20are%20saving%20time%2C%20they'll%20pay%20a%20premium.%20If%20they%20get%20a%20better%20experience%2C%20they'll%20pay%20a%20premium.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicholas%20said%20that%20Sam's%20Club%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20long-standing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffounding-history-of-costco%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarehouse%20club%20business%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20earning%20most%20of%20its%20profits%20from%20membership%20income.%20That%20means%20any%20revenues%20%E2%80%94%20say%2C%20from%20the%20expected%20%24100%20billion%20retail%20media%20advertising%20market%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20reinvested%20in%20the%20business%20i