ion%20between%20President%20Trump%20and%20Mexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-mexico-delayed-month-sheinbaum-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelayed%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Mexico%20tariffs%20by%20one%20month.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheinbaum%20said%20Mexico%20would%20deploy%2010%2C000%20troops%20to%20the%20Mexico-US%20border%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20stem%20the%20flow%20of%20illegal%20fentanyl%20into%20the%20country%2C%20a%20key%20sticking%20point%20for%20Trump's%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20is%20taking%20bold%20action%20to%20hold%20Mexico%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20China%20accountable%20to%20their%20promises%20of%20halting%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20stopping%20poisonous%20fentanyl%20and%20other%20drugs%20from%20flowing%20into%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20tied%20to%20the%20tariffs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20investors%20hope%20that%20a%20similar%20development%20will%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20tariffs%20on%20Canada%20to%20be%20avoided%20or%20delayed.%20Otherwise%2C%20duties%20on%20imports%20from%20Canada%20will%20fully%20go%20into%20effect%20at%2012%3A00%20a.m.%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20and%20President%20Trump%20were%20expected%20to%20speak%20Monday%20afternoon%2C%20continuing%20talks%20from%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftariffs-market-reaction-wall-street-trump-economy-inflation-interest-rates-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsensus%20on%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20the%20proposed%20tariffs%20against%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20will%20likely%20be%20temporary%20if%20they%20are%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20still%20think%20that%20permanent%20tariffs%20on%20the%20US's%20allies%20(Canada%2C%20Mexico)%20wil