3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERichard%20%26quot%3BDick%26quot%3B%20Kramlich%20made%20one%20of%20the%20earliest%20investments%20in%20Apple.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20cofounded%20NEA%20in%201977%2C%20which%20now%20has%20nearly%20%2426%20billion%20in%20assets%20under%20management.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKramlich%20also%20led%20investments%20in%20Juniper%20Networks%2C%20Macromedia%2C%20%2C%20Immunex%2C%20and%20Xoom.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECharles%20Richard%20%26quot%3BDick%26quot%3B%20Kramlich%2C%20cofounder%20of%20VC%20giant%20New%20Enterprise%20Associates%20and%20a%20godfather%20of%20venture%20capital%2C%20passed%20away%20on%20February%201st%20at%20the%20age%20of%2089%2C%20according%20to%20a%20representative%20for%20NEA.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20industry%20has%20lost%20a%20legend%2C%20and%20we%20have%20lost%20a%20cherished%20friend%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20a%20letter%20sent%20from%20NEA%20to%20the%20firm's%20contacts.%20%26quot%3BHe%20led%20investments%20in%20seminal%20companies%20like%20Juniper%20Networks%2C%20Macromedia%2C%20Ascend%20Communications%2C%20Immunex%2C%20Xoom%2C%20Financial%20Engines%2C%20and%20many%20others%3B%20he%20was%20also%20among%20the%20earliest%20investors%20in%20Apple.%20Yet%20the%20true%20magnitude%20of%20his%20impact%20is%20rooted%20in%20his%20visionary%20leadership%2C%20his%20relentless%20curiosity%2C%20and%20his%20hallmark%20tenacity.%20He%20was%20a%20true%20champion%20for%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20that%20long-term%20perspective%20combined%20with%20his%20stalwart%20conviction%20was%20integral%20to%20the%20success%20of%20many%20of%20his%20investments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKramlich%20helped%20start%20NEA%20in%201977%20and%20was%20the%20firm's%20managing%20partner%20for%20its%20first%20seven%20funds.%20He%20helped%20grow%20the%20firm%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20backing%20companies%20like%20Robinhood%2C%20Databricks%2C%20and%20Plaid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20NEA%20has