20risks%20on%20ideas%20that%20seemed%20insane%20at%20the%20time.%20Without%20visionaries%20like%20him%2C%20the%20tech%20world%20wouldn't%20be%20what%20it%20is%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHere's%20the%20full%20letter%20NEA%20sent%20to%20its%20limited%20partners%2C%20employees%2C%20and%20portfolio%20companies%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDear%20partners%2C%20colleagues%2C%20and%20friends%20of%20NEA%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20heavy%20hearts%2C%20we%20are%20reaching%20out%20to%20share%20that%20Charles%20Richard%20%26quot%3BDick%26quot%3B%20Kramlich%2C%20beloved%20co-founder%20of%20NEA%20and%20one%20of%20venture%20capital's%20most%20enduring%20and%20influential%20figures%2C%20passed%20away%20on%20February%201%20at%20the%20age%20of%2089.%20Our%20industry%20has%20lost%20a%20legend%2C%20and%20we%20have%20lost%20a%20cherished%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20true%20pioneer%20of%20venture%20capital%2C%20Dick's%20investing%20career%20began%20in%201969%20as%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Arthur%20Rock%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20He%20was%20captivated%20by%20innovation%20and%20entrepreneurship%20and%20eager%20to%20help%20shape%20the%20nascent%20venture%20capital%20industry.%20When%20he%20co-founded%20NEA%20with%20Chuck%20Newhall%20and%20Frank%20Bonsal%20in%201977%2C%20the%20trio%20set%20out%20to%20form%20a%20%26quot%3B100-year%20partnership%26quot%3B%E2%80%94an%20enduring%20institution%20that%20would%20span%20many%20funds%20and%20flourish%20long%20into%20the%20future%2C%20built%20upon%20shared%20goals%2C%20shared%20values%2C%20and%20shared%20rewards.%20That%20guiding%20principle%20would%20shape%20NEA's%20evolution%20and%20success%20not%20only%20during%20the%20co-founders'%20tenures%2C%20but%20through%20numerous%20successive%20leadership%20transitions%20in%20the%20decades%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Managing%20Partner%20for%20our%20first%20seven%20funds%20and%20a%20General%20Partner%20through%20NEA%2013%2C%20Dick%20was%20instrumental%20in%20many%20of%20NEA's%20most%20successful%20outcomes%20over%20many%20years.%20He%20led%20investments%20in%20seminal%20companies%20like%20Juniper%20Networks%2C%20Macromedia%2C%20Ascend%20Communications%2C%20Immunex%2C%20Xoom%2C%20Financial%20Engines%20and%20many%20others%3B%20he%20was%20also%20among%20the%20earliest%20investors%20in%20Apple.%20Yet%20the%20true%20magnitude%20of%20his%20impact%20is%20rooted%20in%20his%20visionary%20leadership%2C%20his%20relentless%20curiosity%2C%20and%20his%20hallmark%20tenacity.%20He%20was%20a%20true%20champion%20for%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20that%20long-term%20perspective%20combined%20with%20his%20stalwart%20conviction%20was%20integral%20to%20the%20success%20of%20many%20of%20his%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDick%20once%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20think%20venture%20capital%20is%20a%20game%20of%20numbers.%20It's%20not%E2%80%94it's%20a%20game%20of%20courage.%26quot%3B%20That%20wisdom%20continues%20to%20resonate%20within%20our%20firm%20today%2C%20serving%20as%20a%20guiding%20ethos%20as%20we%20navigate%20inevitable%20challenges%2C%20not%20only%20in%20the%20day-to-day%20business%20of%20investing%20but%20as%20we%20continue%20to%20evolve%20our%20firm%20and%20industry%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%20Without%20question%2C%20Dick's%20legacy%20will%20be%20an%20enduring%20one%E2%80%94he%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20not%20only%20on%20venture%20capital%2C%20but%20on%20the%20dozens%20of%20companies%20he%20helped%20build%20and%20the%20countless%20entrepreneurs%20and%20investors%20he%20mentored%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFittingly%2C%20he%20was%20the%20recipient%20of%20countless%20honors%20including%20lifetime%20achievement%20awards%20from%20the%20National%20Venture%20Capital%20Association%20and%20the%20Haas%20School%20of%20Business%20at%20UC%20Berkeley.%20Even%20after%20retiring%20from%20NEA%20in%202012%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20actively%20invest%20as%20a%20co-founder%20of%20Green%20Bay%20Ventures%20and%20as%20CEO%20of%20Kramlich%20Investment%20Group.%20In%20partnership%20with%20his%20wife%20Pamela%2C%20Dick%20was%20also%20a%20prolific%20art%20patron%20and%20collector%E2%80%94together%20they%20built%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20pioneering%20collections%20of%20media%20art%20comprising%20more%20than%20150%20video%2C%20film%2C%20and%20media%20installation%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20his%20wife%20Pamela%2C%20Dick%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20children%20Christina%2C%20Richard%2C%20and%20Mary%20Donna%2C%20and%20many%20grandchildren%E2%80%94all%20of%20whom%20he%20adored%20beyond%20measure.%20Our%20thoughts%20are%20with%20all%20of%20them%20in%20their%20grief%2C%20and%20we%20hope%20they%20are%20comforted%20by%20the%20profound%20impact%20he%20had%20on%20so%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20of%20us%20who%20worked%20alongside%20him%20will%20be%20forever%20grateful%20for%20his%20countless%20contributions%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20celebrate%20his%20many%20achievements%E2%80%94along%20with%20his%20wisdom%2C%20integrity%2C%20and%20humility%E2%80%94for%20decades%20to%20come.%20We%20know%20many%20of%20you%20will%20want%20to%20honor%20Dick's%20extraordinary%20life%20and%20incredible%20impact%20on%20innovation%20and%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20we%20will%20share%20additional%20details%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20are%20available.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frichard-kramlich-cofounder-of-new-enterprise-associates-dies-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738616949000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a125b7bfebcc4d029d97c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frichard-kramlich-cofounder-of-new-enterprise-associates-dies-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Charles%20Richard%20%26quot%3BDick%26quot%3B%20Kramlich%2C%20co-founder%20of%20VC%20firm%20New%20Enterprise%2