20focus%20on%20boosting%20India-US%20cooperation%20in%20trade%2C%20energy%20and%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20phone%20talks%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20Donald%20Trump%20emphasised%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20India%20increasing%20its%20procurement%20of%20US-made%20security%20equipment%20and%20moving%20toward%20a%20fair%20bilateral%20trade%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20already%20indicated%20its%20keenness%20to%20expand%20energy%20ties%20with%20the%20US%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20clean%20energy%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20on%20Saturday%20announced%20plans%20to%20amend%20its%20nuclear%20liability%20law%20and%20set%20up%20a%20nuclear%20energy%20mission%2C%20a%20move%20that%20came%20ahead%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20likely%20visit%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECertain%20clauses%20in%20India's%20Civil%20Liability%20for%20Nuclear%20Damage%20Act%2C%202010%20have%20emerged%20as%20hurdles%20in%20moving%20forward%20in%20implementing%20the%20historic%20civil%20nuclear%20deal%20that%20was%20firmed%20up%20between%20the%20countries%2016%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20said%20to%20be%20looking%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20civil%20nuclear%20cooperation%20with%20the%20US%20in%20small%20modular%20reactors%20(SMRs).%20US-based%20Holtec%20International%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20exporters%20of%20SMRs%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20is%20learnt%20to%20be%20interested%20in%20collaborating%20with%20the%20American%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738607940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F9pufioj_pm-modi-trump-afp_650x400_27_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-likely-to-visit-us-on-february-12-hold-talks-with-donald-trump-say-sources-7627377%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20likely%20to%20visit%20the%20US%20on%20February%2012%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said.%20This%20would%20be%20PM%20Modi's%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20returned%20to%20the%20White%20House.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-likely-to-visit-us-on-february-12-hold-talks-with-donald-trump-say-sources-7627377%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teacher%20In%20South%20Africa%20Cuts%20Off%20Religious%20Thread%20From%20Hindu%20Student's%20Wrist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20teacher%20in%20South%20Africa%20allegedly%20cut%20off%20a%20religious%20thread%20from%20the%20wrist%20of%20a%20Hindu%20student%2C%20triggering%20condemnation%20from%20the%20community%20members%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Binsensitive%20and%20irresponsible%26quot%3B%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20last%20week%20at%20Drakensburg%20Secondary%20School%20in%20KwaZulu-Natal%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20African%20Hindu%20Maha%20Sabha%20(SAHMS)%20has%20called%20for%20action%20by%20education%20authorities%20after%20the%20teacher%20allegedly%20cut%20off%20the%20sacred%20thread%20from%20the%20wrist%20of%20the%20Hindu%20student%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20school%20does%20not%20allow%20wearing%20cultural%20or%20religious%20symbols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SAHMS%20strongly%20condemns%20the%20insensitive%20and%20irresponsible%20action%20of%20an%20educator%20cutting%20off%20a%20religious%20string%20from%20a%20Hindu%20learner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20organisation%20said%20in%20a%20press%20statement%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20said%20it%20is%20investigating%20the%20alleged%20incident%20of%20religious%20intolerance%20at%20the%20school%20but%20the%20probe%20is%20being%20hampered%20as%20the%20victim%20is%20refusing%20to%20come%20forward%20for%20fear%20of%20further%20victimisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAHSM%20president%20Ashwin%20Trikamjee%20said%20both%20the%20principal%20and%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20school's%20governing%20body%20told%20him%20during%20a%20telephonic%20discussion%20that%20they%20were%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20very%20defensive%20about%20not%20allowing%20any%20religious%20discrimination%20at%20their%20school%2C%20both%20declaring%20that%20they%20themselves%20had%20rings%20and%20strings%20on%20their%20hands%2C%20but%20we%20have%20not%20had%20anything%20officially%20in%20writing%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20national%20Indian%20radio%20station%20Lotus%20FM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrikamjee%20recalled%20an%20earlier%20instance%20when%20South%20Africa's%20highest%20judicial%20authority%2C%20the%20Constitutional%20Court%2C%20had%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20Hindu%20student%20who%20was%20debarred%20from%20wearing%20her%20nose%20ring%20by%20her%20school.%20The%20court%20had%20noted%20that%20nobody%20could%20be%20deprived%20of%20exercising%20their%20cultural%20or%20religious%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20incident%20has%20sparked%20inter-religious%20conflict%20in%20the%20area%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20African%20Charter%20of%20Religious%20Rights%20and%20Freedoms%20in%20the%20Constitution%20prohibits%20unfair%20discrimination%20on%20various%20grounds%2C%20including%20religion.%20The%20government%20has%20established%20the%20statutory%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20and%20the%20Cultural%2C%20Religious%20and%20Language%20(CRL)%20Rights%20Commission%20to%20act%20on%20any%20complaints%20related%20to%20discriminatory%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrikamjee%20blamed%20the%20education%20ministry%20for%20failing%20to%20provide%20schools%20with%20clear%20and%20concise%20guidelines%20on%20promoting%20religious%20and%20cultural%20tolerance%2C%20leaving%20them%20uncertain%20about%20what%20is%20acceptable%20and%20what%20is%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Muzi%20Mahlambi%2C%20spokesman%20for%20the%20provincial%20Department%20of%20Education%20in%20KwaZulu-Natal%2C%20where%20over%20two-thirds%20of%20South%20Africa's%20Indian-origin%20citizens%20live%2C%20disagrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Education%20emphasises%20that%20the%20Constitution%20is%20the%20highest%20law%20of%20the%20land%2C%20and%20any%20school%20policy%20that%20contradicts%20it%20is%20unacceptable%2C%20Mahlambi%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20radio%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahlambi%20said%20the%20department%20has%20instructed%20the%20schools%20to%20review%20and%20revise%20their%20codes%20of%20conduct%20and%20policies%20to%20ensure%20they%20align%20with%20the%20Constitution.%20No%20student%20should%20face%20punishment%20for%20their%20religious%20affiliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian-origin%20South%20African%20CRL%20Commissioner%20Raj%20Govender%20said%20if%20anybody's%20religious%20rights%20have%20been%20violated%2C%20they%20can%20approach%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20CRL%20Commission%2C%20I%20think%20the%20school%20needs%20to%20change%20its%20policy%20to%20accommodate%20cultural%20and%20religious%20needs%20of%20the%20minority%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20incident%20of%20the%20alleged%20racial%20discrimination%20at%20the%20Drakensburg%20Secondary%20School%2C%20Govender%20said%20teachers%20should%20remain%20very%20neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20she%20(the%20teacher)%20has%20done%20(what%20is%20alleged)%2C%20she%20has%20seriously%20violated%20her%20role.%20She%20has%20diverted%20from%20her%20real%20role%20as%20an%20educator%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndi